"==== Key mappings
" Clear last search highlighting
nnoremap <Space> :noh<cr>
let mapleader = ","         " Change leader key

"==== Navigating between windows
nnoremap <c-j> <c-w>j
nnoremap <c-k> <c-w>k
nnoremap <c-h> <c-w>h
nnoremap <c-l> <c-w>l

"==== Keep content after pasting
